Sidebar Navigator (sticky right):

Renders buttons [1…20], colored/filled if answered.

Clicking scrolls to #q5 via react-scroll or next/link.

Timer: global countdown in header; on zero auto-submit.

Test Flow
User selects “New Test” → choose “All Domains” or checkboxes per domain.

On start: insert row in tests, set timer, fetch question batch (shuffled within domain only).

On submit or timeout: insert attempts, update tests with scores.

Results Page
Summary: total correct / total, % score badge.

Domain Breakdown: bar chart (Recharts) from score_by_domain.

Review: list each question with user’s choice vs. correct, plus explanation.

Dashboard
Overview cards:

Tests taken, avg score, best domain, last test date.

Table of past tests with link to results.

Score trend line chart.

